This paper deals with the development of a parallel corpus for Portuguese and English languages using the theses and dissertations catalog. The paper involves the use of Statistical Machine Translation (SMT) and Neural Machine Translation (NMT) models for both language directions. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.DL).
